	<!-- EN: Molecular Nutrient Resequencing -->
	<MolecularNutrientResequencing.label>分子營養素重測序</MolecularNutrientResequencing.label>
	
	<!-- EN: Construct Replimat systems, advanced versions of nutrient paste dispensers that convert raw nutritive feedstock into a wider variety of high quality meals. Also automatically lays nutrient feedstock pipelines along existing power conduit networks. -->
	<MolecularNutrientResequencing.description>建造食品合成系統，使儲存的營養原料轉換成各樣的美味食品，同時在現有的電網旁自動鋪設營養原料輸送管道。</MolecularNutrientResequencing.description>
	
	<!-- EN: About: Building a Replimat system -->
	<MolecularNutrientResequencing.discoveredLetterTitle>關於：建造食品合成系統</MolecularNutrientResequencing.discoveredLetterTitle>
	
	<!-- EN: You now have the technology to build a Replimat system.\n\nA typical Replimat setup requires:\n\n  -One Replimat Computer, to control the entire system\n  -One (or more) Replimat Hoppers(s), to convert raw food into nutrient feedstock\n  -One (or more) Replimat Feedstock Tanks(s), to store the nutrient feedstock\n  -One (or more) Replimat Terminal(s), to serve meals to your colonists\n\nHowever, each Replimat Computer requires a special Isolinear Computing Module component. You can collect Isolinear Computing Modules via the following ways:\n\n  -Orbital or caravan exotic goods traders sell Isolinear Computing Modules. Invite or wait for them.\n  -Some quests are rewarded with Isolinear Computing Modules.\n\nOnce you have built a Replimat Computer, you can connect it to multiple Hoppers, Tanks and Terminals via the same power grid to build a comprehensive Replimat system.-->
	
	<MolecularNutrientResequencing.discoveredLetterText>現在你可以建造食品合成系統了。\n\n通常一個食品合成系統需要:\n\n  -一台主電腦，來控制整個食品合成系統\n  -(至少)一個食品合成系統儲料槽，來把生鮮食材轉換成系統用的液體形式營養原料\n  -(至少)一個原料儲存桶，來儲存營養原料\n  -(至少)一個食品合成器，來複製居民要吃的食品\n\n不過，每台主電腦需要一個等線性電腦模塊零件來建造。你可以透過以下幾種方式收集等線性電腦模塊：\n\n -外貿軌道商人或拜訪的外貿貿易旅隊有時候會賣等線性電腦模塊。邀請或等待他們拜訪。\n -有些任務會有等線性電腦模塊作為獎勵。\n\n建造了主電腦之後，你可以透過電線連接到多數的儲料槽，原料儲存桶和食品合成器，组成一个完善的食品合成系統。</MolecularNutrientResequencing.discoveredLetterText>
	
